The '''Democratic Party''' (Spanish: '''''Partido Demócrata''''') was an political party in Cuba. They won 21 out of 57 seats in the Cuban parliamentary [[Cuban parliamentary election, 1942|election 1942]].<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/58051010|title=Elections in the Americas : a data handbook|date=2005|publisher=Oxford University Press|others=Nohlen, Dieter.|isbn=0199253587|location=New York|oclc=58051010}}</ref>
